                </svg>
                <h3>Open Source</h3> All of our project is available on GitHub make sure to fork us!
                <br>
                <a class="btn btn-info block-btn-margin" href="http://github.com/ExtensibleHomeInterface/EHI-Server">View Repo</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 block">
            <div class="text-center block-margin">
                <svg class="icon" style="fill:red">
